}
`}{`[/block]`}</p>
    <p>{`[block:api-header]`}{`
{
"title": "Obtaining the Routing Key"
}
`}{`[/block]`}{`
Once created, the body of the response will contain the integration key or integration email, which can be used to trigger, acknowledge and resolve alerts and incidents in PagerDuty.`}</p>
